title: 820-00165 not turn on
message:
Be sure to use original Magsafe 2 charger.

Post PM_BATLOW_L, PM_DSW_PWRGD, PCH_DSWVRMEN, PM_RSMRST_L, SMC_ADAPTER_EN and the 4 PCH's RTC signals.
